to encrypt:
send nonce,
send associated data length
send associated data
send plaintext length
send plaintext
send command 'e'
then send commnd 'e' to receive following ciphertext

to decrypt
send nonce,

send associated data length
send associated data
send ciphertext length, the length should include the tag
send ciphertext, the tag should be appended at last


send command 'd'
then send command 'd' to receive following plaintext
